snippet.title: Ports of Call gameplay (PC Game, 1987)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Ports of Call, Dos PC game produced by Aegis International in 1987 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/ports-of-call/590/
Exploring the interface and building up the fleet in this maritime management sim.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
